\SE\SE[2] Your Mama is right below. \!\SE[2] I need to make
sure you see my splendid grown-up form...

\SE[2]Do you want to know why things turned out like this?
\SE[3]I can tell you within my knowledge...

\SE[62]I don't want to hear it... \!\SE[45]It doesn't matter
anymore...

\SE[4]W-Wait... Where are you going? \SE[8]You don't have
anywhere to go back to, right?

\SE[0]I don't know about that... \!\SE[57]Everything... I'm
not interested in any of it...

\SE[2]If you're okay with it... Won't you come with me?
\SE[0]I believe I can understand you better than anyone
else.
\SE[60]Being with you... What can I do?

\SE\SE[15]I can do anything! \!\SE[15]With the power of
emotions, anything can be granted!

\SE\SE[15] You have a face that says I can't believe it.
\!\SE[1] Well then, let me show you the proof! \!\SE[15] You
and I can do anything...!

\SE[4]Well then, let's start with some practice moving your
body! \SE[0]Once you grow, you'll be able to do even things
like this. I'll show you solid proof!

\SE[3]Hmm... Where would be a good place to practice...
\SE[2]A place where your 'motivation' can come out would be
nice, don't you think...

\SE\SE[15]I've come up with a good idea...! \!\SE[15]Let's
go meet the person who killed 'Mama'! \!\SE[16]That way,
your 'motivation' will come out too, right!

\SE[46]Ah... You made a really nice face just now, didn't
you...? \SE[15]In that case, there's no need to hesitate.
\SE[1]Rest assured. I'll go with you too.

Let's... kill everything together? Everything that denies
you... everything...
